      "contentTrack": "Shared",
      "flowPurpose": "Mind's eye and room",
      "text": "Bring your attention to your mind's eye and imagine the room you are in.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_INT_100_MINDS_EYE_ROOM_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_INT_100_MINDS_EYE_ROOM_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 4
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C002",
      "role": "instruction",
      "order": 200,
      "priority": "p0",
      "contentTrack": "Retrospection",
      "text": "Replay in your mind how you arrived here.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_200_REWIND_FEW_MINUTES_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_200_REWIND_FEW_MINUTES_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 3
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C003",
      "role": "instruction",
      "order": 210,
      "priority": "p0",
      "contentTrack": "Retrospection",
      "text": "Now go a little further back. Notice what happened just before that.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_210_REWIND_BIT_EARLIER_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_210_REWIND_BIT_EARLIER_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 5
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C004",
      "role": "instruction",
      "order": 220,
      "priority": "p0",
      "contentTrack": "Retrospection",
      "text": "Continue moving backward through your day. Let the memories appear at their own pace.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_220_REWIND_CONTINUE_DAY_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_220_REWIND_CONTINUE_DAY_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 5
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C005",
      "role": "instruction",
      "order": 230,
      "priority": "p1",
      "contentTrack": "Retrospection",
      "text": "If any moment brings up emotion, simply observe it.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_230_NOTICE_EMOTIONS_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_KM_INS_230_NOTICE_EMOTIONS_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 3
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C006",
      "role": "reminder",
      "order": 290,
      "priority": "p0",
      "contentTrack": "Shared",
      "text": "Move through your memories at a natural pace. There is no need to rush or slow anything down.",
      "voices": {
        "Asaf": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_RW_REM_290_MOVE_NATURAL_PACE_ASAF.mp3",
        "Dan": "modules/evening_visualization_fractional/asaf/EV_RW_REM_290_MOVE_NATURAL_PACE_ASAF.mp3"
      },
      "durationSec": 6
    },
    {
      "clipId": "EVK_C007",
      "role": "reminder",
      "order": 300,
      "priority": "p1",
      "contentTrack": "Retrospection",
      "text": "If your mind drifts, gently continue from where you left off.",
